<%- include('layout') %>

<title><%= title %></title>
<%- include('navbar') %>

<div class="container">
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12 ms-4 " style="font-family: Georgia, serif;">
        <p style="color: #1e1915; font-size: 36px;">Recently posted books</p>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-3">
                    <a href="#" class="image-link">
                        <img src="https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1694006777i/197577126._SX150_.jpg" alt="Description of the image" class="image">
                    </a>    
                </div>                
                <div class="col-md-8 new-releases mb-5">
                    <div class="mb-1 book-number">#1</div>
                    <div class="mb-1" >
                        <a class="text-decoration-none book-description" href="">
                            This Summer Will Be Different
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-1" >
                        <a class="text-decoration-none book-authur" href="">
                            Carley Fortune
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-1" >
                        <i style="color: #e87400;" class="bi bi-star"></i> <span class="rating" >4.26</span>
                    </div>
                    <button class="btn fw-bold mt-2 mb-1 btn-want-to-read" style="background-color: #3f8363; color: #ffffff; border-radius: 15%;">Want to read</button>
                    <p class="mb-2 content" id="expandable-content">
                        This summer they’ll keep their promise. This summer they won’t give into temptation. This summer will be different. 
                        <br>
                        Lucy is the tourist vacationing at a beach house on Prince Edward Island. Felix is the local who shows her a very good time. The only problem: Lucy doesn’t know he’s her best friend’s younger brother. Lucy and Felix’s chemistry is unreal, but the list of reasons why they need to stay away from each other is long, and they vow to never repeat that electric night again.
                    </p>
                    <div class="show-more-button">
                        <a style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; color: #1e1915;" class="text-decoration-none" href="#">
                            Show more  &#9662;
                        </a>  
                    </div>
                </div>
                
            </div>
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                <!-- Horizontal line to the left -->
                <hr class="flex-grow-1 mr-3" style="border-top: 2px solid #767676;">
        
                <button type="submit" class="btn fs-6 read-more-button mb-5" style="color: #ffffff;" onclick="showMoreBooks()">Show more books</button>
        
                <!-- Horizontal line to the right -->
                <hr class="flex-grow-1 ml-3" style="border-top: 2px solid #767676;">
            </div>
        </div>    
    </div>
</div>
</div>
<script>
    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
        var showMoreButtons = document.querySelectorAll(".show-more-button");
    
        showMoreButtons.forEach(function(button) {
            button.addEventListener("click", function() {
                var expandableContent = this.closest(".row").querySelector(".content");
                expandableContent.style.height = "auto";
                this.style.display = "none";
            });
        });
    });
    </script>
    